<p>Dreaming of an argument with your mother indicates the emergence of hardship, and other interpretations, which we will explain for single women, married women, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant women </a> </a> </a> , divorced women, such as verbal arguments with the mother, fighting and shouting with the mother, or the mother arguing with her daughter, or arguing with my daughters, or my mother hitting me on the hand <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> </a> </a> and more on the subject:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of arguing with the mother in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing <strong>arguments with the mother in a dream</strong> does not indicate good at all, and it indicates the emergence of some problems that the person will face in his family, and because of the mistakes that this person makes, they will cause sadness and worry for his parents.<br/>Dreaming of arguing with the mother also indicates people who do not know the value of their parents while they are alive, and their regret increases when they lose them, and they must try to please them and thus get their prayers for them.  with kindness.</p>
<p>Whoever argues with his mother in a dream means that he will not see good in his work and his environment will be filled with people who only want their benefit from him, this indicates that the person is two-faced and deceitful. .<br/>This dream also expresses that the person's actions will be astray and the doors of wealth will close in front of him, and from an Islamic perspective, this dream indicates that the person may not have children and stand beside sins and sin.  sins instead of doing good deeds, and the person must repent to God and ask for forgiveness and forgiveness.<br/>If anyone sees <strong>arguing with a dead mother in a dream</strong>, it indicates that the person neglects his duties as a son and that he upset his mother in her life, and for this reason, his actions may not go as he wants.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
