</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شجار-مع-أم-في-المنام?page=2665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شجار-مع-أم-في-المنام?page=2665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شجار-مع-أم-في-المنام?page=2665" > an argument with a mother </a> </a> </a> in a dream shows people who do everything after consulting their mothers and are always connected to them.</p>
<p>Arguments with the mother, then regret in the dream, which means that because of some words that were said without that person's knowledge, and then he will regret and apologize to the person he has towards.  The person receives the prayers of his parents for good, and that he reconciles with them, earns their hearts, trusts them again, and does more for that.</p>
<p>Arguing with the mother, then slapping the mother on the person in the dream indicates that the person is retreating from an act that may not bring him good, and it is a warning from the father and mother to him, and an indication that he did not do it for support.  from his family towards him, he would not have retreated from the paths of error, but he would always remain protected by their support and protection.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
