</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In the case of arguing with the mother, then reconciliation, after the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/وفاة-الأم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3660" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/وفاة-الأم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3660" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/وفاة-الأم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3660" > death of the mother </a> </a> </a> in a dream, this indicates that the person will receive good news and meet someone he loves very much, and from an Islamic perspective, then the person should recite Fatiha for her, spend charity on her soul and do righteous deeds, because this dream indicates that the person must pray for the mother as well.</p>
<p>Seeing reconciliation with the mother in a dream expresses the excellence of good for the person and an indication that the dreamer will receive a lot of wonderful news and that this person will be loved by everyone in his environment and will be highly respected. <br/>This dream means that this person and his emotional or family relationships will always be positive and reassuring, and he will have a respectable business personality and everyone will trust him in the market, and it also expresses the wonderful and happy changes that the person will get soon and will always remain satisfied with himself.  .</p>
<p>Arguing and reconciling with the mother, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-احتضان-الأم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3269" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-احتضان-الأم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3269" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-احتضان-الأم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3269" > embracing the mother </a> </a> </a> and kissing her in the dream, if the mother is alive, this means that the dreamer will meet the person as soon as possible and get rid of the heartache and longing.  You have good news soon.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
