</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing the mother arguing with the brothers, whether they are male or female, this vision is praiseworthy and not strange, which indicates the good relationship between you and your sisters, God willing.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of arguing with the mother in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> </a> </a></span></h2>
<p>If you saw an argument with your mother in a dream, then this vision predicts conflicts in real life that are caused by your foolish and reckless actions.</p>
<p>And the unmarried girl, if she argues with her mother in a dream, this is a warning that she will get into an awkward situation that will not only affect her life, but will also affect the lives of her relatives, and dream interpreters recommend that you abandon your current plans and spend some time among your family members.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
