</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Dream interpreters also warn <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> </a> </a> that you should now refuse entertainment gatherings or dates with friends and take care of your family.</p>
<p>If a married woman sees that her mother is scolding her in a dream, this means that she should be careful about fleeting pleasures and encounters with another man, otherwise her husband will find out about everything.</p>
<p>Seeing a young man <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-شاب-في-المنام-للنابلسي?page=3252" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-شاب-في-المنام-للنابلسي?page=3252" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-شاب-في-المنام-للنابلسي?page=3252" > or woman </a> </a> </a> fighting with their mother in a dream means that they will face conflicts in the house and the dreamer will be the cause of these conflicts.  To avoid such situations, it is best to listen to the advice of your parents.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
